{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c3e68a305f","title":"对打击入侵美军飞机对策报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e3210921c5","index":0,"year":1955,"month":5,"day":10,"articleId":"c3e68a305f"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[{"id":"3fa63bc243","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c3e68a305f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东对中国人民解放军总参谋长菜裕1955年5月10日报告的批语。"},{"id":"f5b9f32c24","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c3e68a305f","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"菜裕的报告汇报了美军飞机侵入我安东（丹东）以南地区领空与我机空战的情况，并判断美机仍有来犯进行挑鲜之可能。提出我方对策为：当查明美机北上时，我机即进入待机空域巡逻监视其行动。如美机入侵至我领空及保卫目标上空时，则组织所有防空兵力火器坚决打击之。要求安东、旅大地区的空军密切协同动作，以确保我军机场及保卫目标的安全。周恩来5月10日批示：“今日美机入侵，我即还击，刻已发消息警告美方。总参部署方针，请主席批示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"61f94032dd","type":"title","text":"对打击人侵美军飞机对策报告的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c3e68a305f"},{"id":"3fa63bc243","type":"paragraph","text":"照办。1）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c3e68a305f"},{"id":"f5b9f32c24","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c3e68a305f"},{"id":"849094bc43","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c3e68a305f"}],"page":{"id":"3fdd8005f6","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c3e68a305f","start":71,"end":71}}}},"__N_SSG":true}